同样的乐器差别怎么就这么大呢","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"5751","username":"euphonium","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"5497","dbdateline":"1480676693","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"34359414","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"水边井","authorid":"264153","dateline":"2016-12-2 19:18","message":"用腿来演戏，你京强！","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"5752","username":"水边井","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"5498","dbdateline":"1480677519","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"34359448","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"neverMJ","authorid":"104706","dateline":"2016-12-2 19:24","message":"比起啰嗦的晴香部长，香织算管的少的啦","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"5753","username":"neverMJ","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"5499","dbdateline":"1480677855","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"34359650","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"darkddragon","authorid":"394146","dateline":"2016-12-2 19:48","message":"如果说第五集是京吹二季的面子，高密度地演出比赛的紧张与窒息，最后一口气淋漓尽致的将情感爆发出来，那这集就是这部片的里子了，各种各样的情感相互纠缠在一起，通过分镜和各种细微动作展现着某些无法明说的情感和心绪，让人忍不住去来回揣测。明明每个人都勇敢的将自己所想的，平时提起来还会有点尴尬的想法说了出来，以各自的方式努力寻求着互相理解，最后随着明日香的独奏而完结，情感悠长地发泄了出来，但很多事情还是无法改变，看着真让人觉得有些憋屈。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"5754","username":"darkddragon","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"5500","dbdateline":"1480679317","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"34359697","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"jellyfis","authorid":"261623","dateline":"2016-12-2 19:55","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><font color=\"#999999\">neverMJ 发表于 2016-12-2 19:24</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#999999\">比起啰嗦的晴香部长，香织算管的少的啦</font></div><br />\n很明显明日香是享受被晴香啰嗦的","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"5755","username":"jellyfis","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"5501","dbdateline":"1480679737","groupiconid":